2024-11-25 15:29:00.997 +05:30 [INF] Executed DbCommand (36ms) [Parameters=[@__username_0='?' (Size = 50)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[AadharNumber], [s].[Email], [s].[IsActive], [s].[LoginAt], [s].[LogoutAt], [s].[PanNumber], [s].[Password], [s].[UserName], [s].[Id0], [s].[AccountHolderName], [s].[Address], [s].[CreatedAt], [s].[DateOfBirth], [s].[PhoneNumber], [s].[UpdatedAt], [s].[UserId], [s0].[RolesId], [s0].[UsersId], [s0].[Id], [s0].[Name]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [u].[Id], [u].[AadharNumber], [u].[Email], [u].[IsActive], [u].[LoginAt], [u].[LogoutAt], [u].[PanNumber], [u].[Password], [u].[UserName], [u0].[Id] AS [Id0], [u0].[AccountHolderName], [u0].[Address], [u0].[CreatedAt], [u0].[DateOfBirth], [u0].[PhoneNumber], [u0].[UpdatedAt], [u0].[UserId]
    FROM [Users] AS [u]
    LEFT JOIN [UserProfiles] AS [u0] ON [u].[Id] = [u0].[UserId]
    WHERE [u].[UserName] = @__username_0
) AS [s]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [r].[RolesId], [r].[UsersId], [r0].[Id], [r0].[Name]
    FROM [RoleUser] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Roles] AS [r0] ON [r].[RolesId] = [r0].[Id]

) AS [s0] ON [s].[Id] = [s0].[UsersId]

    SELECT TOP(1) [u].[Id], [u].[AadharNumber], [u].[Email], [u].[IsActive], [u].[LoginAt], [u].[LogoutAt], [u].[PanNumber], [u].[Password], [u].[UserName], [u0].[Id] AS [Id0], [u0].[AccountHolderName], [u0].[Address], [u0].[CreatedAt], [u0].[DateOfBirth], [u0].[PhoneNumber], [u0].[UpdatedAt], [u0].[UserId]
    FROM [Users] AS [u]
    LEFT JOIN [UserProfiles] AS [u0] ON [u].[Id] = [u0].[UserId]
    WHERE [u].[UserName] = @__userRecovery_UserName_0 AND [u].[Email] = @__userRecovery_Email_1 AND [u].[Password] = @__userRecovery_Password_2
) AS [s]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [r].[RolesId], [r].[UsersId], [r0].[Id], [r0].[Name]
    FROM [RoleUser] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Roles] AS [r0] ON [r].[RolesId] = [r0].[Id]
) AS [s0] ON [s].[Id] = [s0].[UsersId]
ORDER BY [s].[Id], [s].[Id0], [s0].[RolesId], [s0].[UsersId]

CREATE TABLE [Accounts] (
    [AccountId] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [AccountTypeId] int NOT NULL,
    [UserId] int NOT NULL,
    [BranchId] int NOT NULL,
    [StatusTypeId] int NOT NULL,
    [AccountNumber] bigint NOT NULL,
    [Balance] decimal(10,2) NOT NULL,
    [CurrentInterestRate] decimal(5,2) NOT NULL,
    [CurrentMonthlyFee] decimal(10,2) NOT NULL,
    [CreatedAt] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [UpdatedAt] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [IsActive] bit NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Accounts] PRIMARY KEY ([AccountId]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Accounts_AccountTypes_AccountTypeId] FOREIGN KEY ([AccountTypeId]) REFERENCES [AccountTypes] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Accounts_Branches_BranchId] FOREIGN KEY ([BranchId]) REFERENCES [Branches] ([BranchId]) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Accounts_StatusTypes_StatusTypeId] FOREIGN KEY ([StatusTypeId]) REFERENCES [StatusTypes] ([StatusTypeId]) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Accounts_Users_UserId] FOREIGN KEY ([UserId]) REFERENCES [Users] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE

CREATE TABLE [Notifications] (
    [Id] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [UserId] int NOT NULL,
    [Title] nvarchar(200) NOT NULL,
    [Message] nvarchar(1000) NOT NULL,
    [StatusId] int NOT NULL,
    [CreatedAt] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [SentAt] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Notifications] PRIMARY KEY ([Id]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Notifications_StatusTypes_StatusId] FOREIGN KEY ([StatusId]) REFERENCES [StatusTypes] ([StatusTypeId]) ON DELETE CASCADE,

    SELECT [r].[RolesId], [r].[UsersId], [r0].[Id], [r0].[Name]
    FROM [RoleUser] AS [r]
